(Prerequisite: jump out of GFW first since it uses Google Charts)

First, install the extension in Chrome
	enter "chrome://extensions"
	click "Load unpacked extension" button and select the file folder of this extension
	
Then, choose a NBA match from http://sports.sina.com.cn/nba/live/
	click "实录", and you'll jump to the live page of the match
	for example, http://sports.sina.com.cn/nba/live.html?id=2014031616

Finally, click the NBA icon! Time-score chart is right here!